Only hang-ups and people not interested.

We are switching to a new list in 4 minutes!
Good, yeah Nevada calls last night were really bad
lots of people annoyed with calls and wrong numbers
I've called NV before last night, and I had similar issues. I'm not sure why so many people are actually located on the east coast or while they're answering unknown numbers if woken up from sleep!
Like a couple of weeks ago, even. It's not just you and not just last night.
I think it's just the nature of the type of area Neveda & Las Vegas is - lots of movement in & out.
Just keep dialing, it helps clean the list, even if people hang up.
